Year: # Year: Year of the calendar week according to ISO 8601
# Week: Calendar week according to ISO 8601
# Ending: Last day of the week (Sunday)
# NoDeaths_EP: Number of deaths in Switzerland of persons residing in Switzerland with extrapolation for the last 40 days
# Expected: Number of deaths expected this week compared to the same week in previous years
# LowerB: Lower limit of the expected range at 99% of the expected value
# UpperB: Upper limit of the expected range at 99% of the expected value
# Diff: Weeks when the number of deaths exceeds the upper limit of the expected range, the difference between the observed minus the expected number is shown
